[{"id": 92374, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5189, "text": "(Ya Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259r!) M\u00fcnafiql\u0259r (riyakarlar) s\u0259nin yan\u0131na g\u0259ldikl\u0259ri zaman: \u201cBiz s\u0259nin, do\u011frudan da, Allah\u0131n Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259ri oldu\u011funa \u015f\u0259had\u0259t veririk! \u2013 deyirl\u0259r. Allah s\u0259nin Onun h\u0259qiqi Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259r oldu\u011funu bilir. Allah h\u0259m d\u0259 m\u00fcnafiql\u0259rin xalis yalan\u00e7\u0131 olduqlar\u0131na \u015f\u0259had\u0259t verir."}, {"id": 92375, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5190, "text": "Onlar (yalan) andlar\u0131n\u0131 \u00f6zl\u0259rind\u0259 sip\u0259r edib (xalq\u0131) Allah yolundan d\u00f6nd\u0259rirl\u0259r. H\u0259qiq\u0259t\u0259n, onlar\u0131n t\u00f6r\u0259tdikl\u0259ri \u0259m\u0259ll\u0259r nec\u0259 d\u0259 pisdir!"}, {"id": 92376, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5191, "text": "Bunun s\u0259b\u0259bi odur ki, onlar (dild\u0259) iman g\u0259tirdil\u0259r, sonra is\u0259 (\u00fcr\u0259kl\u0259rind\u0259 gizli) kafir oldular. Buna g\u00f6r\u0259 d\u0259 onlar\u0131n \u00fcr\u0259kl\u0259rin\u0259 m\u00f6h\u00fcr vurulmu\u015f, \u00f6zl\u0259ri is\u0259 anlamaz kims\u0259l\u0259r olmu\u015flar."}, {"id": 92377, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5192, "text": "(Ya Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259r!) S\u0259n onlar\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fckd\u0259 c\u00fcss\u0259l\u0259ri (boy-buxunlar\u0131, g\u00f6z\u0259llikl\u0259ri) xo\u015funa g\u0259lir, dan\u0131\u015fanda s\u00f6zl\u0259rin\u0259 qulaq as\u0131rsan. Onlar, sanki (divara) s\u00f6yk\u0259dilmi\u015f dir\u0259kl\u0259rdir (ruhsuz b\u0259d\u0259n, m\u00fcq\u0259vva kimidirl\u0259r). Onlar (iki\u00fczl\u00fcl\u00fckl\u0259rinin Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259r\u0259 v\u0259 m\u00f6\u2019minl\u0259r\u0259 \u0259yan olaca\u011f\u0131ndan qorxub) h\u0259r bir q\u0131\u015fq\u0131r\u0131\u011f\u0131n (s\u0259s-k\u00fcy\u00fcn) \u00f6z \u0259leyhl\u0259rin\u0259 oldu\u011funu z\u0259nn edirl\u0259r. Onlar d\u00fc\u015fm\u0259ndirl\u0259r, s\u0259n onlardan h\u0259z\u0259r et! Allah onlar\u0131 \u00f6ld\u00fcrs\u00fcn, nec\u0259 d\u0259 haqdan d\u00f6nd\u0259rilirl\u0259r!"}, {"id": 92378, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5193, "text": "Onlara: \u201cG\u0259lin Allah\u0131n Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259ri (R\u0259bbinizd\u0259n) sizin ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma\u011f\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 dil\u0259sin!\u201d \u2013deyildiyi zaman (istehza il\u0259) ba\u015flar\u0131n\u0131 bulayar v\u0259 s\u0259n (Ya R\u0259sulum!) onlar\u0131n t\u0259k\u0259bb\u00fcrl\u0259 \u00fcz \u00e7evirdikl\u0259rini g\u00f6r\u0259rs\u0259n."}, {"id": 92379, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5194, "text": "S\u0259n onlar\u0131n ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanmas\u0131n\u0131 dil\u0259s\u0259n d\u0259, dil\u0259m\u0259s\u0259n d\u0259, f\u0259rqi yoxdur. Onsuz da Allah onlar\u0131 ba\u011f\u0131\u015flamayacaqd\u0131r. \u015e\u00fcbh\u0259siz ki, Allah fasiq q\u00f6vm\u00fc do\u011fru yola y\u00f6n\u0259ltm\u0259z!"}, {"id": 92380, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5195, "text": "Onlar: \u201cAllah\u0131n Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259ri yan\u0131nda olanlara bir \u015fey verm\u0259yin ki, da\u011f\u0131l\u0131b getsinl\u0259r!\u201d \u2013 dey\u0259n kims\u0259l\u0259rdir. Halbuki g\u00f6yl\u0259rin v\u0259 yerin x\u0259zin\u0259l\u0259ri Allaha m\u0259xsusdur, lakin m\u00fcnafiql\u0259r (bunu) anlamazlar."}, {"id": 92381, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 488, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5196, "text": "Onlar: \u201c\u018fg\u0259r biz (B\u0259ni M\u00fcst\u0259liq vuru\u015funda) M\u0259din\u0259y\u0259 qay\u0131tsaq, \u0259n g\u00fccl\u00fcl\u0259r (\u0259n \u015f\u0259r\u0259flil\u0259r \u2013 m\u00fcnafiql\u0259r) \u0259n z\u0259ifl\u0259ri (\u0259n h\u0259qirl\u0259ri \u2013 Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259ri v\u0259 ona iman g\u0259tir\u0259nl\u0259ri), \u0259lb\u0259tt\u0259, oradan \u00e7\u0131xardacaqlar!\u201d \u2013 deyirl\u0259r. Halbuki \u015f\u0259r\u0259f-\u015fan da, (q\u00fcvv\u0259t v\u0259 q\u0259l\u0259b\u0259 d\u0259) yaln\u0131z Allaha, Onun Pey\u011f\u0259mb\u0259rin\u0259 v\u0259 m\u00f6\u2019minl\u0259r\u0259 m\u0259xsusdur, lakin m\u00fcnafiql\u0259r (bunu) bilm\u0259zl\u0259r!"}, {"id": 92382, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 489, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5197, "text": "Ey iman g\u0259tir\u0259nl\u0259r! N\u0259 mal-d\u00f6vl\u0259tiniz, n\u0259 d\u0259 o\u011ful-u\u015fa\u011f\u0131n\u0131z sizi Allah\u0131n zikrind\u0259n yay\u0131nd\u0131rmas\u0131n! H\u0259r k\u0259s bunu ets\u0259 (Allah\u0131 yada salmasa), bel\u0259l\u0259ri \u0259sl ziyana u\u011frayanlard\u0131r."}, {"id": 92383, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 489, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5198, "text": "Birinizin \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fc \u00e7at\u0131b: \u201cEy R\u0259bbim! M\u0259n\u0259 bir az m\u00f6hl\u0259t vers\u0259ydin, s\u0259d\u0259q\u0259 verib salehl\u0259rd\u0259n olard\u0131m! \u2013 dem\u0259mi\u015fd\u0259n \u0259vv\u0259l siz\u0259 verdiyim ruzid\u0259n (Allah yolunda) x\u0259rcl\u0259yin."}, {"id": 92384, "identifier": "az.mammadaliyev", "surah_number": 63, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0646\u0627\u0641\u0642\u0648\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Al-Munaafiqoon", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Hypocrites", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 555, "ruku": 489, "hizb_quarter": 222, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "az", "name": "M\u0259mm\u0259d\u0259liyev & B\u00fcnyadov", "transelator_en_name": "Vasim Mammadaliyev and Ziya Bunyadov", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5199, "text": "V\u0259 (bilin ki) Allah \u0259c\u0259li \u00e7atan he\u00e7 k\u0259s\u0259 m\u00f6hl\u0259t verm\u0259z. Allah sizin n\u0259 etdikl\u0259rinizd\u0259n x\u0259b\u0259rdard\u0131r!"}]